            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1513716892,
            "creation_date": 1513716892,
            "body": "<p>You're using getKey() on your base blog DB reference (/Blog). You need to create a new node within that reference with push(), and then getKey() on your newly created child.<\/p>\n\n<p><code>final String id = mDatabase.push().getKey();<\/code><\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 47895037,
            "question_id": 47894887
        }
